Program 2.2
To write a JS program using the if…….else statement.
Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
       <title>if else statement</title>
</head>
<body>
 <script>
    var a = 7;
if
    (a % 2 == 0)
    document.write("Even Number");
    else
    document.write("Odd Number");
 </script>   
</body>
</html>


Program 2.3
To write a JS program using the else…….if statement.

Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
       <title>if else Statement</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        var marks = 85;
        if (marks >= 75)
            document.write("Distinction");
        else if (marks >= 60)
            document.write("First Class");
        else
            document.write("Pass");
    </script>
</body>
</html>


Program 2.4
To write a JS program using switch statement.

Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
       <title>Switch Statement</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        var day = 8;
        switch(day) {
        case 1: document.write("Monady");
            break;
        case 2: document.write("Tuesday");
            break;
        case 3: document.write("Wednesday");
            break;
        case 4: document.write("Thrusday");
            break;
        case 5: document.write("Friday");
            break;
        case 6: document.write("Saturday");
            break;
        case 7: document.write("Sunday");
            break;
        default: document.write("Invalid Day");
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>


