Program 2.7
Write a JS program to demonstrate do…while loop.
Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<head></head>
<body>
<script>
var i=2;
do{
  document.write(i + "<br>");
  i++
}while(i <= 10);
</script>
</body>
</html>


